name: A possible landscape 04 (60x84)
description: The possible landscapes are chunks of imaginary topographies made by an algorithm and drawn by a robot. This file is the vector source file used to create a physcial drawing, and is complementary to https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/114144 You will receive this 1/1 OBJKT for free once 114144 is purchased. If the original drawing is ever stolen or damaged, it can be recreated with a plotter machine (Axidraw extended is recommended) from the svg.
